submission_title: It’s Exciting as a first year and gets more Horrifying each year
author: Deckowner
body: It's especially hard when you are out of the country for the summer. I still remember how I had a queue of like 20 something back up course plans and frantically enrolling courses while swapping between the plans as some courses got filled up. the urge to punch my screen as I click enroll but it returns and error after loading for 5 mins was real.

body: I feel like I’m on Tickestmaster or something every time I do course enrollment
